Purpose: A randomized simulation of the two heroes' (Timothy and Harold) escape from the pit. 
         View 'Purpose' and 'Usage' in 'main.cc' for further details

Files: main.cc random.cc Escape.cc Hero.cc PartArray.cc Participant.cc Pit.cc Position.cc Snorc.cc
    Escape.h Hero.h PartArray.h Participant.h Pit.h Position.h Snorc.h defs.h README Makefile

Instructions: 
Run in a linux environment. Enter the directory with the necessary files. 

Enter "make" into the terminal.

Enter "./a4" next. This will launch the simulation